 	    SHORT="Abuse-SDL is a port of Abuse by Crack Dot Com"
 cat << EOF
Abuse-SDL is a port of Abuse by Crack Dot Com to Linux using the Simple DirectMedia Layer library. 
This allows Abuse to run at screen depths greater than 8bpp as well as fullscreen. 
Features
 Abuse-SDL has the following extra features over the original Abuse:
 - Run at any screen depth from 8bpp to 32bpp.
 - Run fullscreen or in a window.
 - Software and OpenGL hardware accelerated scaling.
 - Lock the mouse to the window.
 - Mousewheel support for changing weapons.
 - Stereo sound.
 EOF
 

